author: Jacob_Wilson
title: LEGO World City 9274 Community Workers - The Review
review: I do own this set, but a lot of the pieces are missing, and I don't know where they are! - But I am trying to find them. Most of the minifigures are rubbish like the FireFighters are from the late 1990's LEGO System Sets, but my favourite are the Police Offices from the LEGO World City Sets and the minifigure with the pizza top on is called Pepper and the others like him is from LEGO Island Xtreme Stunts.
